Package: MethyLiution
Type: Package
Title: MethyLiution: A QC Pipeline For Methylation Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Chunlao Tang, Yupeng Li, Karim Malki, David Collier, Brian Eastwood, Yushi Liu, Neil Pearson
Maintainer: Neil Pearson <pearson_neil@network.lilly.com>
Description: Carry out a number of quality control operations on methylation data from 450K or EPIC microarray experiments. Compute a consistent set of quality metrics. Account for and correct some common mistakes.
